---
title: Korean Inspired Bulgogi King Prawn Rice Bowl with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Pickled Carrot Ribbons
description: Named after Korea's most well-known BBQ dish, bulgogi sauce has a sweet and smoky flavour, thanks to its mix of soy, garlic, brown sugar and pear & apple purees. Bulgogi is a perfect match for rice and noodle dishes or even as a flavour driver in tacos.

A popular condiment in many Asian countries, sambal paste's vibrant heat is perfect for boosting flavour in our Asian style dishes. This paste contains herbs and spices such as red chillies, lemongrass and tamarind, making it the perfect flavour driver for both veggie and meat dishes alike.
